<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Admin Login - College Assistant</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .login-wrapper {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 420px;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .login-card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 40px;
      box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    }
    .login-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .login-header h2 {
      color: #f8fafc;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .login-header p {
      color: #94a3b8;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    .form-floating > label {
      color: #94a3b8;
    }
    .form-control {
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.5);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      color: #f8fafc;
      border-radius: 12px;
    }
    .form-control:focus {
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.8);
      border-color: #6366f1;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1);
      color: #f8fafc;
    }
    .form-control::placeholder {
      color: transparent; /* Needed for floating labels to work perfectly */
    }
    .btn-login {
      background: #6366f1;
      color: white;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 14px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: none;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .btn-login:hover {
      background: #4f46e5;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.4);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="login-wrapper">
    <div class="login-card">
      <div class="login-header">
        <h2>Admin Portal</h2>
        <p>Sign in to manage the Chatbot</p>
      </div>

      {{#if errorMessage}}
      <div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert" style="background: rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.5); color: #fecaca; border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 14px;">
        {{errorMessage}}
      </div>
      {{/if}}

      <form action="/Login" method="POST">
        <div class="form-floating mb-3">
          <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" name="email" placeholder="name@example.com" required>
          <label for="email">Email address</label>
        </div>
        <div class="form-floating mb-3">
          <input type="password" class="form-control" id="password" name="password" placeholder="Password" required>
          <label for="password">Password</label>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-end mb-4">
          <a href="#" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#forgotPasswordModal" style="color: #94a3b8; font-size: 13px; text-decoration: none; transition: 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.color='#f8fafc'" onmouseout="this.style.color='#94a3b8'">Forgot Password?</a>
        </div>
        <button class="btn btn-login w-100" type="submit">Sign In</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Forgot Password Modal -->
  <div class="modal fade" id="forgotPasswordModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="forgotPasswordModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered">
      <div class="modal-content" style="background: #1e293b; color: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 16px;">
        <div class="modal-header" style="border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);">
          <h5 class="modal-title" id="forgotPasswordModalLabel" style="font-weight: 600;">Password Recovery</h5>
          <button type="button" class="btn-close btn-close-white" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-body" style="font-size: 15px; color: #cbd5e1; line-height: 1.6;">
          <p>Because your Admin Panel is secured using strict Environment Variables for deployment safety, passwords cannot be reset automatically.</p>
          <p><strong>To view or change your password:</strong></p>
          <ol class="mb-3">
            <li class="mb-2">Log in to your hosting provider's dashboard (e.g., Render, Vercel, or Heroku).</li>
            <li class="mb-2">Navigate to your project's <strong>Environment Variables</strong> settings.</li>
            <li class="mb-2">Locate the <code style="background: #0f172a; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; color: #38bdf8;">ADMIN_PASSWORD</code> variable to view or update your credentials.</li>
          </ol>
          <p class="mb-0" style="font-size: 13px; color: #94a3b8;"><em>If running locally, please check the <code>.env</code> file in your project's root directory.</em></p>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-footer" style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);">
          <button type="button" class="btn" style="background: #6366f1; color: white; border-radius: 8px; padding: 8px 16px; font-weight: 500;" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Got it</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
